You get out of the way, okay?

794
00:43:00,680 --> 00:43:01,680
Okay.

795
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:02,880
You think you're so pretty?

796
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:14,960
Cut.

797
00:43:17,160 --> 00:43:18,680
Oh, I am exhausted.

798
00:43:20,800 --> 00:43:21,640
The printer is broken.

799
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:22,880
I send print jobs but nothing comes out.

800
00:43:22,880 --> 00:43:23,880
I already called a technician.

801
00:43:24,680 --> 00:43:25,680
His name is Boom.

802
00:43:26,800 --> 00:43:28,520
Please check the printer...

803
00:43:28,520 --> 00:43:29,520
What’s wrong with your tongue?

804
00:43:31,200 --> 00:43:33,200
If your mouth is too tight, then don’t talk.

805
00:43:34,240 --> 00:43:36,760
This is the new fish.
Shouldn’t we give a welcome?

806
00:43:37,280 --> 00:43:38,280
No!

807
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:40,480
My eyes are burning, Sergeant.

808
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:41,920
I am not a sergeant.

809
00:43:42,680 --> 00:43:45,440
I am Inspector Akkarin Thanapuwadech.

810
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:46,800
I was framed.

811
00:43:46,800 --> 00:43:47,840
I will listen to you.

812
00:43:47,840 --> 00:43:49,800
But please make sure it is the truth.
